QueryText: Management of White backed plant hopper.
KCCAns: I suggest him to spray Trifos 40 EC @ 2 ml per litre of water.

QueryText: ASKING ABOUT NUTRIENT SUPPLIMENT  IN CABAGE.
KCCAns: SUGGESTED TO SPRAY TRACEL @ 2 GM/LITER OF WATER
I suggest him to apply 50 kg FYM,UREA- 560 g, SSP -320 g ,MOP-1200 g and BORAX-250 g.
RECOMMENDED HIM TO BUY AND  SPRAY CHLORPYRIFOS 2ML/LT OR INDOXACARB 1ML/LT OR SPINOSAD 45 SC 1ML/2LT OF WATER THREE TIMES IN 15 DAYS INTERVAL

QueryText: Management of cabbage caterpillar in Radish.
KCCAns: I suggest him to spray Chlorpyriphos 20 EC @ 2 ml per litre of water.

QueryText: ASKING CONTROL MEASURE OF LEAF HOPPER IN CABBAGE CULTIVATION
KCCAns: SPRAY EKALUX @ 2 ML PER LITRE OF WATER
